          <title>
            <string language="en">Cross section of a root</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Querschnitt einer Wurzel</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Coupe d'une racine</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Seção transversal de uma raiz</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Sezione trasversale di una radice</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Διαγώνιο τμήμα μιας ρίζας</string>

          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This illustration shows a cross section of a root showing the different tissues including stele, pericycle, root hairs, cortex, xylem, endodermis and phloem.</string>
          </description>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Diese Abbildung zeigt einen Querschnitt einer 
Wurzel, welche die unterschiedlichen Gewebe einschließlich Stele, 
pericycle, Wurzelhaare, Rinde, xylem, endodermis und Phloem zeigt.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cette illustration montre une coupe d'une racine 
montrant les différents tissus comprenant le stele, le pericycle, les
poils de racine, le cortex, le xylem, les endodermis et le phloème.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Esta ilustração mostra uma seção transversal 
de uma raiz que mostra os tecidos diferentes including o stele, o 
pericycle, os cabelos da raiz, o cortex, o xylem, os endodermis e o 
phloem.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questa illustrazione mostra una sezione 
trasversale di una radice che mostra i tessuti differenti compreso lo 
stele, il pericycle, i capelli della radice, la corteccia, il xylem, i
endodermis ed il floema.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτή η απεικόνιση εμφανίζει διαγώνιο τμήμα μιας 
ρίζας που εμφανίζει τους διαφορετικούς ιστούς συμπεριλαμβανομένου
stele, τις pericycle, τρίχες ρίζας, το φλοιό, το ξύλημα, τα 
endodermis και φλοίωμα.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Esta ilustración muestra una sección transversal
de una raíz que muestra los diversos tejidos finos incluyendo el 
stele, el pericycle, los pelos de la raíz, la corteza, el xylem, 
endodermis y el líber.</string>
          </description>
